{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"XPathExpression.evaluate()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression/evaluate","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression\"><code>XPathExpression</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><em><code>evaluate()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>evaluate()</code></strong> method of the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression\"><code>XPathExpression</code></a> interface executes an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath\">XPath</a> expression on the given node or document and\n  returns an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathResult\"><code>XPathResult</code></a>.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>XPathResult node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">evaluate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>contextNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> type<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> result<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"contextnode\">contextNode</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> representing the context to use for evaluating the expression.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"type\">type <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      Specifies the type of result to be returned by evaluating the expression. This must\n      be one of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathResult#constants\" title=\"XPathResult\"><code>XPathResult.Constants</code></a>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"result\">result <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      Allows to specify a result object which may be reused and returned by this method.\n      If this is specified as <code>null</code> or the implementation does not reuse the\n      specified result, a new result object will be returned.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>\n  An <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathResult\"><code>XPathResult</code></a> object representing the result of evaluating the XPath\n  expression.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"invalid_expression_err\">INVALID_EXPRESSION_ERR</h4>\n<p>\n  If the expression is not legal according to the rules of the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator\"><code>XPathEvaluator</code></a>, an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathException\"><code>XPathException</code></a> of type\n  <code>INVALID_EXPRESSION_ERR</code> is raised.\n</p>\n<h4 id=\"type_err\">TYPE_ERR</h4>\n<p>\n  In case result cannot be converted to the specified type, an\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathException\"><code>XPathException</code></a> of type <code>TYPE_ERR</code> is raised.\n</p>\n<h4 id=\"namespace_err\">NAMESPACE_ERR</h4>\n<p>\n  If the expression contains namespace prefixes which cannot be resolved by the specified\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathNSResolver\"><code>XPathNSResolver</code></a>, a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> of type\n  <code>NAMESPACE_ERROR</code> is raised.\n</p>\n<h4 id=\"wrong_document_err\">WRONG_DOCUMENT_ERR</h4>\n<p>\n  If the provided context node is from a document that is not supported by the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator\"><code>XPathEvaluator</code></a>, a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> of type\n  <code>WRONG_DOCUMENT_ERR</code> is raised.\n</p>\n<h4 id=\"not_supported_err\">NOT_SUPPORTED_ERR</h4>\n<p>\n  If the provided context node is not a type permitted as an XPath context node or the\n  request type is not permitted by the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator\"><code>XPathEvaluator</code></a>, a\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> of type <code>NOT_SUPPORTED_ERR</code> is raised.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following example shows the use of the <code>evaluate()</code> method.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>XPath example<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Number of <span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"<\">&amp;lt;</span>div<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\">\">&amp;gt;</span>s: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> xpath <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"//div\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> evaluator <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XPathEvaluator</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> expression <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> evaluator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createExpression</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"//div\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> result <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> expression<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">evaluate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> XPathResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">ORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"output\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>snapshotLength<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result_2","title":"Result","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"400\" height=\"70\" src=\"http://localhost:5042/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression/evaluate/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-xpathexpression-evaluate","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.XPathExpression.evaluate"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.XPathExpression.evaluate","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression/evaluate/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The evaluate() method of the\n  XPathExpression interface executes an XPath expression on the given node or document and\n  returns an XPathResult.","popularity":0,"modified":"2021-09-14T18:08:09.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xpathexpression/evaluate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/xpathexpression/evaluate/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/2279e5ae6c229c707a014a22aa1ec4635a0f981f","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression","title":"XPathExpression"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression/evaluate","title":"XPathExpression.evaluate()"}],"pageTitle":"XPathExpression.evaluate() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}